author: FourFourTwo
description: Leroy Sane will have an operation on his nose that will keep him out of Germany's Confederations Cup plans.
title: Germany winger Sane out of Confederations Cup

description: Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan was confronted by key allies France and Germany with diplomatic complaints despite him traveling to Brussels to celebrate the unity of the NATO alliance.
title: Turkey's leader confronted by France, Germany at NATO summit

author: Griff Witte, Karla Adam, Souad Mekhennet, Griff Witte, Karla Adam, Souad Mekhennet
description: Authorities are trying to find out why the bomber was in Germany just days before the attack.
title: Manchester bombing probe expands to Germany amid raids, arrests in Britain

author: Lizzie Dearden
description: The Manchester bomber visited Germany just four days before launching his attack, it has been revealed. Intelligence sources told Focus Online Salman Abedi flew from the city of Düsseldorf to Manchester, but was not on an international database or a list of potential Islamists being tracked through Europe.
title: Manchester bomber was in Germany four days before the attack

author: Robin Emmott and John Irish
description: France and Germany will agree to a U.S. plan for NATO to play a bigger role in the fight against Islamic militants at a meeting with President Donald Trump on Thursday, but insist the move is purely symbolic, four senior European diplomats said.
title: France, Germany to agree to NATO role against Islamic State: diplomats

author: Von FOCUS-Online-Autorin Pia Kienel, FOCUS-Online-Redakteurin Alina Bähr
description: Was für ein Finale: Céline erkämpft sich den Titel „Germany’s next Topmodel 2017“. Kurz vor der Entscheidung gab es allerdings einige Pleiten, Pech und Pannen. Alle Infos rund um das Finale finden Sie in unserem News-Ticker.
title: "GNTM"-Finale: Céline ist „Germany’s next Topmodel 2017“

author: FOCUS Online
description: Céline Bethmann aus Koblenz hat es geschafft: Sie ist "Germany's next Topmodel" 2017! Die 18-jährige gewann in der Finalshow am Donnerstagabend nicht nur einen Modelvertrag, sondern auch 100.000 Euro in bar. FOCUS Online erlebte Célines großen Moment live in der Arena in Oberhausen - und auch sonst noch allerlei Kuriositäten, die die TV-Kameras nicht zeigten.
title: "Germany's next Topmodel" 2017: Heiratsantrag und Handy-Safe: Was Prosieben im TV nicht zeigte

description: He was speaking in Germany, which knows a thing or two about walls.
title: Barack Obama Throws Shade At Donald Trump: 'We Can't Hide Behind The Wall'

author: Von Focus Magazin-Autorin Beate Strobel
description: Finale der 12. Suche nach „Germany’s Next Topmodel“: In Oberhausen treten vier Mädchen gegeneinander an, und nur eine von ihnen kann Deutschlands Schönste für ein Jahr werden. Also alles wie gehabt: mehr Glitzer als Spannung, mehr Zeit als Inhalt und mehr Klum denn je.
title: TV-Kolumne „Germany’s Next Topmodel“: Mehr Glitzer als Spannung, mehr Zeit als Inhalt und mehr Klum denn je
